Both list pages default statusFilter to 'all', which exposes draft and archived rooms/problems to students browsing the catalog. Students should see only published content by default. Content managers and platform admins should see all statuses. The fix is a one-line initial state: useState<ContentStatus | 'all'>(canAuthor ? 'all' : 'published').

