23. List page search input has no debounce
RoomsPage, CoursesPage, and ProblemsPage all update search state on onChange. The q param is sent to the backend on every character change (since useInfiniteQuery re-runs when the query key changes). This is 3× worse than the search page issue because it's an infinite query, not a simple query. A 300ms debounce on the search inputs would reduce server load substantially.

